#id=1
#text=A few months ago , I went to the library to check out a couple of books .
#id=2
#text=Our local library is very large and full of very interesting books , magazines and movies .
#id=3
#text=Before I went to find my books , I stopped at the coffee shop in the library .
#id=4
#text=I ordered a coffee and a blueberry muffin so I could have a snack .
#id=5
#text=Once I finished my snack , I began to look for my books .
#id=6
#text=I used the library 's computer to find the location of each book .
#id=7
#text=Finding the books only took me about 10 minutes .
#id=8
#text=After I found the books , I sat down in a comfortable chair that was next to a lamp .
#id=9
#text=I began reading one of my books while I was drinking my coffee .
#text=I stayed at the library and read for about thirty minutes .
#text=I went to the checkout to check out my books , and then I left to walk home .
